Isaiah 1-6 <t><f>ⓡ</f> From the sole of the foot even to the head, </t><t>there is no soundness in it, </t><t>but bruises and sores </t><t>and raw wounds; </t><t>they are <f>ⓢ</f>not pressed out or bound up </t><t>or softened with oil. </t>
